&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brigands Perch&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Brigand&amp;rsquo;s Perch is a haven for thieves, cutthroats, and highwaymen near the main travel hubs of the neutral island. It&amp;rsquo;s a bandit refuge for levels 10 - 20 tucked into the mountains and led by a former dishonored knight of Ambreka.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Docs: Duskvale</title><link>https://www.fallofanempire.com/docs/locations/the-severed-isles/candus-neutral/duskvale/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Jan 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.fallofanempire.com/docs/locations/the-severed-isles/candus-neutral/duskvale/</guid><description>
&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Duskvale&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Once a Meroei farmstead built under the protection of a noble knight&amp;rsquo;s keep, Duskvale has now become the home of an undead epidemic. A dark necromancer has taken up residence there and now controls the once living citizens as his undead minions. (levels 30 - 40)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Faction = The Blighted id 98&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>Docs: Skyforge</title><link>https://www.fallofanempire.com/docs/locations/the-severed-isles/candus-neutral/skyforge/</link><pubDate>Wed, 04 Jan 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://www.fallofanempire.com/docs/locations/the-severed-isles/candus-neutral/skyforge/</guid><description>
&lt;div class=&#34;pageinfo pageinfo-primary&#34;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Skyforge&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
